This is a playground for me to try different tech.

Basic approach: tons of javascript speaking JSON to a server.  Server only speaks JSON, and HTML pages are few. (screw links)

Feature outline:
 1. main screen
  1. current system
  1. what planets you can travel to
  1. what systems you can travel to
  1. ship / cargo summary
 1. planet screen
  1. market (buy/sell goods)
  1. shop (buy/sell ship parts)
  1. dealership (buy/sell ships)

Tech to try
 1. JQuery
 1. Huchentoot for serving
 1. Elephant for persistence
 1. more adw-charting
 1. more vecto for drawing maps
 1. various AI libraries